{
  "id": "RAW_3f78e3",
  "title": "被网友逼着改名的谷歌 Nano Banana，正在抢 99%时尚博主的饭碗 ｜ 机器之心",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-09-05-8",
  "date": "2025-09-05 07:30:49",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section>\n   <section>\n    <blockquote>\n     <p>谷歌听劝。</p>\n    </blockquote>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p>上周，谷歌给 Nano Banana 改了个正儿八经的名字，网友一片哗然，疯狂吐槽新名字 Gemini 2.5 Flash Image 又长又无聊，完全没有记忆点。</p>\n  <p>好在谷歌听劝。</p>\n  <p>有眼尖的网友发现，谷歌已经悄悄把 AI Studio 里 Gemini 2.5 Flash Image 的名字换回了 Nano Banana。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_ba2570\" data-ratio=\"0.4962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1184\" data-height=\"588\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"287\" data-imgfileid=\"503505186\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/42a6179d-3597-4d1f-ad0d-18fb1e42c1f4/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>甚至还有网友提议，以后所有 AI 模型都用水果和蔬菜来命名，这样更有趣，也比<span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">那些</span> AI 公司一贯糟糕又拗口的命名方式要好得多。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-backh=\"161\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"322\" data-imgfileid=\"503505187\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094257_d4c570\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/937f9829-c1bc-44c1-b82d-25ba84f5ba89/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>言归正传。</p>\n  <p>前几天我们<a data-itemshowtype=\"0\" data-linktype=\"2\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&amp;mid=2650988112&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=85e9c4eb578cdf9b4ee5d4c401c44345&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\">盘点了 Nano Banana 的七种神仙玩法</a>，其中呼声最高的就是生成 OOTD 这一趴。</p>\n  <section data-id=\"91330\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n   <section>\n    <section data-role=\"animate\" data-width=\"100%\">\n     <section data-divisor=\"1\" data-width=\"200%\">\n      <section data-width=\"50%\">\n       <section>\n        <section>\n         <img data-imgfileid=\"503505190\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_4c8bbc\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/6c8e5590-7b62-4ab5-bb9c-ac0ec557bc1f/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"50%\">\n       <section>\n        <section data-width=\"100%\">\n         <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"YqCydUGySoHa0IxaRMwccG5xnMh\">\n          <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;e396aa40-d4fb-4779-8805-4436e05ea699&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:282.984375,&quot;width&quot;:418.671875,&quot;currHeight&quot;:282.984375,&quot;currWidth&quot;:418.671875,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:730,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1080,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.6759259259259259,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FYBzDbFEYZocqVQxeN3mcwtamnBe%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;YBzDbFEYZocqVQxeN3mcwtamnBe&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:622737,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n           <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_b9a4b1\" data-ratio=\"0.6759259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"730\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"391\" data-imgfileid=\"503505189\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;width: 100%;\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f969bff0-8507-4aec-9e80-d1d4439c696f/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p>所以，今天我们索性就来一期「砸」时尚博主饭碗的整活特辑。</p>\n  <p><strong>生成明星 OOTD</strong></p>\n  <p>「OOTD」 是 Outfit of the Day 英文缩写，意思是今日穿搭。</p>\n  <p>如果你经常混迹 ins、微博、小红书，就会发现明星们也很爱晒穿搭照片，倪妮、舒淇、高圆圆、钟楚曦都是出了名的私服大户。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\">\n   <section data-id=\"91330\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n    <section>\n     <section data-role=\"animate\" data-width=\"100%\">\n      <section data-divisor=\"1\" data-width=\"400%\">\n       <section data-width=\"25%\">\n        <section>\n         <section data-width=\"100%\">\n          <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"YqCydUGySoHa0IxaRMwccG5xnMh\">\n           <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;db82abcb-6a65-4bb8-b112-5091528155f1&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:137.5546875,&quot;width&quot;:91.703125,&quot;currHeight&quot;:137.5546875,&quot;currWidth&quot;:91.703125,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1620,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1080,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.6759259259259259,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FV7qFbVetToBGF8xaCwDcRzManwg%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;V7qFbVetToBGF8xaCwDcRzManwg&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:2449848,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n            <img data-height=\"1620\" data-imgfileid=\"503505239\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_e7b942\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100% !important;\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ca247a7c-b766-4d70-a0d3-447f22debdd5/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section data-width=\"25%\">\n        <section>\n         <section data-width=\"100%\">\n          <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"YqCydUGySoHa0IxaRMwccG5xnMh\">\n           <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;c1b9efdd-b609-4270-93ce-deb5af247b67&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:137.546875,&quot;width&quot;:91.7578125,&quot;currHeight&quot;:137.546875,&quot;currWidth&quot;:91.7578125,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1619,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1080,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.6759259259259259,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FPMf8brM6WoMLSTxwOG8chimMnpf%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;PMf8brM6WoMLSTxwOG8chimMnpf&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1728878,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n            <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_6b4b72\" data-ratio=\"1.499074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1619\" data-imgfileid=\"503505235\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f1c74654-f2aa-4cbc-bff0-335327d3d7c9/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section data-width=\"25%\">\n        <section>\n         <section data-width=\"100%\">\n          <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"YqCydUGySoHa0IxaRMwccG5xnMh\">\n           <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;8c7f89ca-b42a-4839-8227-657aea5b88fd&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:137.546875,&quot;width&quot;:91.1953125,&quot;currHeight&quot;:137.546875,&quot;currWidth&quot;:91.1953125,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1086,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:720,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1.0138888888888888,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FHdYRbN3RqoTGVPxhaPhcCeOUnVh%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;HdYRbN3RqoTGVPxhaPhcCeOUnVh&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1127361,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n            <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094257_cc0d17\" data-ratio=\"1.5083333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"720\" data-width=\"720\" data-height=\"1086\" data-imgfileid=\"503505238\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3deb6e34-964d-4960-b81a-8c9bc811406a/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section data-width=\"25%\">\n        <section>\n         <section data-width=\"100%\">\n          <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"YqCydUGySoHa0IxaRMwccG5xnMh\">\n           <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;9c8d9c56-ba59-4079-9a0f-f8f2f2904539&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:137.5546875,&quot;width&quot;:91.703125,&quot;currHeight&quot;:137.5546875,&quot;currWidth&quot;:91.703125,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1620,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1080,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.6759259259259259,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FJvgnb9CgjouZ6KxOGgMcyHionsg%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;Jvgnb9CgjouZ6KxOGgMcyHionsg&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:2501616,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n            <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094257_cc40cc\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1620\" data-imgfileid=\"503505236\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100% !important;\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3229ca78-2ccc-42e3-92b2-f41cd2f1b1c4/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p>很多时尚博主就专门收集她们的穿搭照，整理成一份份清单，方便时髦精们跟着明星学穿搭。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_0e9cd5\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1440\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"771\" data-imgfileid=\"503505240\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b4092af5-79c8-42e4-b8b6-691a3e31d565/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"8\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>但这是个苦力活，每一步都是耗费心力的大工程：</p>\n  <ul>\n   <li>\n    <p>从大量零散的活动照、街拍图里找出清晰可用的明星造型图；</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>逐一识别衣服、鞋子、包包和配饰等单品来源；</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>在最短时间里整理清单内容，把单品的品牌名、具体型号、参考价格甚至购买渠道一一标注；</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>最后还要做视觉设计，将明星造型图和单品对照图排版在一张图里，配上简洁的说明和价格标签。</p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>而且这个圈子也是相当卷，明星造型更新速度非常快，博主必须争分夺秒抢发布，否则就会被其他账号捷足先登，失去传播价值。</p>\n  <p>现在有了 Nano Banana，工作流程就简单多了。</p>\n  <p>以倪妮一次活动私服为例。</p>\n  <p>打开 Google AI Studio，选择 Nano Banana，上传参考图，输入提示词：</p>\n  <p>Generate a flat lay OOTD outfit image from a top-down perspective based on the uploaded reference photo, ensuring that the clothing, accessories, and shoes are replicated 1:1 from the reference.（请根据上传的参考照片，生成一张俯拍平铺的 OOTD 穿搭图，服装、配饰、鞋子需与上传的参考照片 1:1 复刻）</p>\n  <p>链接：https://aistudio.google.com/</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-backh=\"242\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"503505307\" data-ratio=\"0.41759259259259257\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_5f60a6\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f1b46012-74ca-43d6-aba5-e021e1c3d34c/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"9\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>为了生成结果更准确，可以多丢几张各种角度和姿势的参考图。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094257_b38b06\" data-ratio=\"0.44814814814814813\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"259\" data-imgfileid=\"503505309\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"11\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/6dd1ef2b-8533-491a-a9c6-43f822b27c06/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"10\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;图1和图2为参考图，图3为Nano Banana生成的OOTD</sup></p>\n  <p>Nano Banana 可以精准捕捉穿搭细节，比如不对称剪裁、下摆流苏、露肩设计、酒红色长裙以及黑色尖头短靴都被准确复刻。</p>\n  <p>当然也有小 bug，比如针织衫显得不够修身，金色圆形珍珠耳坠也对不上号。</p>\n  <p>下面这一套 OOTD 整体生成效果也不错，只不过原图中的微喇西装裤，在生成图里被偷换成了直筒裤。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_43168c\" data-ratio=\"0.6759259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"391\" data-imgfileid=\"503505265\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"12\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/715736e4-97fd-4fae-bf1a-5749af0f8470/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"11\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 左图为参考图，右图为 Nano Banana 生成的 OOTD</sup></p>\n  <p>我们还可以把提示词润色得更详细一些，生成效果也更好：</p>\n  <p>From the uploaded reference photo, extract the outfit and recreate it as a high-quality top-down flat-lay OOTD board. Requirements:</p>\n  <ul>\n   <li>\n    <p>Include only the visible clothing and accessories from the reference: top, bottom, shoes, and jewelry if present.</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>Keep colors, textures, and silhouettes accurate to the original outfit.</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>Arrange the pieces neatly in a balanced composition: tops at the top, bottoms centered, shoes placed symmetrically below, accessories arranged to the sides.</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>Use a clean, neutral background (light beige or warm fabric texture) to highlight the outfit.</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>Show realistic fabric folds, natural shadows, and detailed textures.</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>Present the result in a modern editorial style suitable for fashion magazines or social media posts.</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>Do not add extra props, models, or logos.</p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p>Output in high resolution with crisp edges and consistent lighting.</p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_832e5e\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"434\" data-imgfileid=\"503505267\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"13\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/c25d7c79-7880-489f-89a3-e4f091dc2a7f/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"12\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094257_e3bd8e\" data-ratio=\"0.600925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"347\" data-imgfileid=\"503505268\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"14\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/55655162-9113-40fc-a954-4aea2a795491/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"13\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_7a7068\" data-ratio=\"0.4703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"272\" data-imgfileid=\"503505269\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"15\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/a5ccbe22-0b3f-4899-ac2f-64e3c4b87ad3/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_747a59\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"433\" data-imgfileid=\"503505270\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0943fda2-aca7-4c3f-8cf4-f8146acc3618/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>再来个进阶版本，让它生成一张带有品牌名称标注的舒淇造型清单图。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094257_b34745\" data-ratio=\"0.7416666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"429\" data-imgfileid=\"503505272\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ce1d73d2-d9f9-4603-a39b-338a45f5b409/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"16\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>结果发现，Nano Banana 一次性生成成功概率很低：要么听不懂指令，要么就是拆解后的单品货不对版、品牌名称标注错误。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-backh=\"867\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"1024\" data-imgfileid=\"503505273\" data-ratio=\"1.499267935578331\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_2674f1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"683\" data-width=\"683\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"18\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f4796f85-2408-4760-b463-af31de88cef3/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"17\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p><sup>输入提示词：Generate a celebrity OOTD outfit checklist by identifying and breaking down each item, including clothing and accessories. Then, create an outfit breakdown image with the brand name written below each item, and include a reference price if available (omit the price if it cannot be found).Nano Banana 将礼服和配饰的品牌名称全部识别错误。</sup></p>\n  <p>我们换了个思路，分两步走：</p>\n  <p>第一步，打开 Gemini 2.5，上传图片，询问「图中的礼服和珠宝分别来自哪个品牌？」Gemini 2.5 正确识别出礼服来自阿玛尼，珠宝来自宝格丽。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-backh=\"484\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"1054\" data-imgfileid=\"503505274\" data-ratio=\"0.8361111111111111\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_bc2276\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1260\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"19\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/2210fed6-56c5-4ab5-ac5e-a7f23a95385d/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"18\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>第二步，输入提示词：请根据上传的参考照片，生成一张俯拍平铺的 OOTD 穿搭图，服装需与上传的参考照片 1:1 复刻，背景为浅粉色，并在裙子的下方写上品牌名称 “Armani Privé“，在配饰下方写上品牌名称 “BVLGARI”。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-backh=\"433\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"503505276\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_db8a90\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"20\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/48676503-8c53-470d-96e3-ce1974eb64d4/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"19\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>虽然能实现，但流程略显繁琐。期待未来 Nano Banana 能一步到位，直接生成带有准确品牌名称标注的造型清单图。</p>\n  <p><strong>一键换衣</strong></p>\n  <p>每当看上一件好看的高定礼服，粉丝们往往第一时间就会在评论区疯狂 @ 自家明星，希望他们能穿上同款惊艳全场。</p>\n  <p>于是，明星的造型师们就得绞尽脑汁，想办法去借，甚至不惜托关系、排队等候。然而，高定礼服本就难借，还存在合不合身、是否适合本人气质的现实问题。</p>\n  <p>现在，有了这款「一键换衣」神器，一切就变得简单多了。</p>\n  <p>我们上传一张迪丽热巴半身照和一张 AI 生成的紫色礼服图片，输入提示词：让这个人穿上上传的紫色礼服，背景换成欧式建筑前，就能立刻看到明星换装后的效果。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094257_16cdf4\" data-ratio=\"0.5259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"304\" data-imgfileid=\"503505278\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"21\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/4c7ccda2-1a82-4a64-a914-dac7526ff270/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"20\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>也可以使用英文提示词：Change the outfit with the uploaded one，生成结果贴合度极高，几乎挑不出毛病。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_b02982\" data-ratio=\"0.524074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503505280\" data-original-style=\"width: 578px;height: 303px;\" data-index=\"22\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/7a9bd6a0-a13a-4e37-984b-685cd630ca78/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"21\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>除了 OOTD 和换衣，还有网友解锁了更多玩法，比如给设计线稿上色、让设计草图登上 T 台等。</p>\n  <p>X 博主 @ZHO_ZHO_ZHO 丢给 Nano Banana 一个动漫角色，让其变成线稿手绘图，我们可以看到，生成的线稿图保留了角色的姿势和服装细节。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-backh=\"828\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"1011\" data-imgfileid=\"503505281\" data-ratio=\"1.4320113314447591\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_a6f344\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"706\" data-width=\"706\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"23\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/2fb657f0-f8a0-49a8-82df-b6e355ecac1e/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"22\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>再继续上传线稿图和色卡，输入提示词：准确使用色卡为图二人物上色。</p>\n  <p>Nano Banana 就能根据色卡方案，为角色的发色和服装配色进行全套替换。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_4c51c5\" data-ratio=\"1.0435413642960814\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"689\" data-width=\"689\" data-height=\"719\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"603\" data-imgfileid=\"503505282\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"24\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/cd726664-1566-4f07-99f0-9b72427ead9f/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"23\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>底下有网友用同样的方法尝试了另一种色卡，生成效果也很惊艳。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_15f335\" data-ratio=\"0.6444444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"373\" data-imgfileid=\"503505290\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"25\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/1c2771ca-a0b8-4f21-807e-11752de3da97/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"24\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>网友 Yana Welinder 则用 Nano Banana 将一张服装设计草图，转换成时装秀成品。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905094258_730d0e\" data-ratio=\"0.6759259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503505288\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"26\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/7ecdf35c-8857-48ff-b90c-786d399fd791/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"25\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>在过去，时尚创意的呈现往往需要冗长的流程与大量人力投入，而现在，AI 生成技术让这个周期被极大压缩。</p>\n  <p>在不久的将来，像 Nano Banana 这样的工具，不仅能帮设计师更快试验灵感、让造型师提前预览效果，也能让普通人轻松尝试不同风格，找到属于自己的穿搭灵感。</p>\n  <p>你还开发出哪些 Nano Banana 更多好玩的场景？评论区聊聊啊～</p>\n  <p><sup>参考链接：</sup></p>\n  <p><sup>https://x.com/op7418/status/1961703552512118925</sup></p>\n  <p><sup>https://x.com/ai_for_success/status/1962426574399320412</sup></p>\n  <p><sup>https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1960652077891510752</sup></p>\n  <p><sup>https://x.com/yanatweets/status/1961451861934051726</sup></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细展示了谷歌 Nano Banana（Gemini 2.5 Flash Image）在时尚内容创作领域的多种创新应用，包括生成 OOTD 和一键换装。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细展示了谷歌 Nano Banana（Gemini 2.5 Flash Image）在时尚内容创作领域的多种创新应用，包括生成 OOTD 和一键换装。",
  "summary": "本文深度探讨了谷歌 AI 模型 Nano Banana（即 Gemini 2.5 Flash Image）在时尚领域的实际应用，尤其聚焦于如何利用其生成 OOTD（今日穿搭）和实现一键换装。文章首先介绍了 Nano Banana 有趣的命名背景，随后通过明星穿搭的案例，详细演示了如何使用 Google AI Studio 和精确的提示词，将明星街拍图转化为平铺的 OOTD 清单，大大简化了时尚博主的传统工作流程。同时，文章还展示了 AI 模型在服装设计线稿上色、设计草图转时装秀成品等创意领域的潜力。尽管在品牌识别和一次性生成复杂指令方面仍有改进空间，但 Nano Banana 已展现出颠覆时尚内容创作模式的巨大潜力，预示着 AI 技术将极大压缩创意周期，赋能设计师和普通用户。",
  "mainPoints": [
